  "body": "### Description\r\nWhen in archive mode, with V4 database (#2181) only store finalised states periodically based on the `--data-state-snapshot-distance` setting (#2180).\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* Finalised states are only recorded at most every `data-state-snapshot-distance` slots.\r\n* Do not regenerate states we don't have just to store them\r\n* If the snapshot distance falls on an empty slot, then store the state from the last slot that had a block\r\n\r\nPart of #1965 ",
